        <sponsor name-id="S346">Mr. Lee</sponsor>(for himself,<cosponsor name-id="S355">Mr. Cruz</cosponsor>, and<cosponsor name-id="S348">Mr. Paul</cosponsor>) introduced the following bill; which was
